sequenceDiagram
    participant browser
    participant server

    Add something and click "Save"

    browser->>browser: JS handles click event
    browser->>browser: Prevent form default submit
    browser->>browser: Create note object (content + date)
    browser->>browser: Add note to local state and re-render UI

    browser->>server: POST https://studies.cs.helsinki.fi/exampleapp/new_note_spa
    activate server
    Note right of server: Server stores the new note
    server-->>browser: 201 Created (JSON response)
    deactivate server

    Note right of browser: No page reload â€” SPA stays active
